general_provisions: This bill enacts provisions related to property loss related to homelessness.
hilighted_provisions: This bill:<hr><ltbullet>defines terms;<hr><ltbullet>enacts provisions related to property loss related to homelessness; <hr><ltbullet>creates the Property Loss Related to Homelessness Compensation Enterprise Fund (fund);<hr><ltbullet>describes allowable uses of the fund;<hr><ltbullet>provides that money in the fund is nonlapsing;<hr><ltbullet>provides for a sunset review by July 1, 2028.
